      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nesconset%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "The commercial heart of Nesconset shifted to Smithtown Boulevard between Old Nichols Road and Southern Boulevard as summer residences grew.",
